
Within the STM32MP1 series, youâ€™ll find variants. Some options:

STM32MP151: Single Cortex-A7 core + M4. 
STM32MP153: Dual Cortex-A7 + M4. 
STM32MP157: Dual A7 cores + M4 + possibly GPU/display features. 

Recommendation: If you want maximum flexibility (Linux plus MCU plus possibly graphics/display) go for the MP157 variant. 
		        If you want simpler/cheaper, MP151 is fine.